    Megatron sniffed the air around the doors to the great cavern. So far 
they had not met any troble...but they had just gotten to the cave after all. 
Waspinator also buzzed frantically around the cavern.
    "How do we get in, Megatron?" Waspinator said in his insect bizz voice. 
He was getting on the tyrants nerves.
    Megatron didnt answer, but instead rapped on the door and waited for an 
answer.

    Aracnia looked to her new....um...intrest, Quickstrike. She had indeed 
made new improvements on the base....but tarantulas was missing.
    "Have you seen Tarantulas at all, Quickstrike? Aerostreak?" She asked, 
looking around the room.

    Tarantulas dumped Darkmouse onto the ground at the mouth of the bunker. 
She would be safe here, for now he had other things to do.
